    "body": "I get the warning mentioned in the title of this issue.\r\n\r\nI have the latest version of Cython 0.52.2 and Python   (v2.7.12:d33e0cf91556, Jun 27 2016, 15:24:40) [MSC v.1500 64 bit (AMD64)]\r\n\r\nNot sure how to add debugging or reproducing information, I'm trying to compile a more complex file.\r\n\r\nThe offending line in my generated .c file is:\r\n\r\nif ((8 * sizeof(unsigned long) < 53) || (2 * PyLong_SHIFT < 53) || (a < (double) (1L<<53))) {\r\n\r\nso it seems to try to shift 53 positions in a Long value",
